<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>“春天的思念”专场音乐会</strong></span><strong> </strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2013</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">4</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">6</span>日<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>晚<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">19:30</span></span> </p>
 
<p style="text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;"> <br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> 一、男声独唱《山歌唱出好兆头》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                         </span>郑南词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>饶荣发曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                         《咱老百姓》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                     </span>张俊以、云剑词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>戚建波曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                     演唱：周韡<br /></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">        二、女声独唱《对花》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                   </span>戏歌</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《高山流水》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                     </span>韩静霆词 羊鸣曲</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;"> <span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                              演唱：李研心 </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、原生态演唱《天下黄河》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                               </span>山西民歌</span></p>
<p> <span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            《山丹丹开花红艳艳》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                               </span>陕北民歌</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;"> <span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                              演唱：陈建强（星光大道无冕之王）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、二胡独奏《二泉映月》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                   </span>华彦钧曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                       演奏：付琼</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、</span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">女高音独唱《我和我的祖国》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                         </span>张藜词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>秦咏诚曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            《平安是福》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                     </span>晓成词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>友殿曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                      演唱：陈笑玮</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">六、</span>男高音独唱《怀念战友》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                           </span>雷振邦词曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            《父母在家就在》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                          </span>车行词 戚建波曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                            演唱：张向华（文化部优秀剧目展演获奖者）</span></p>
