<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                  演唱：李研心<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>赵健 </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、男中音独唱《我是中国人》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                              </span>石飞词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>谷建芬曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                     演唱：赵健</span></p>
