<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                           《春风圆舞曲》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                           </span>吕金藻词 尚德义曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                           演唱：谢琳（国家一级演员）</span></p>
