<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                   演奏：张学琴</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十一、男女声二重唱《紫藤花》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                   </span>王泉、韩伟词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>施光南曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                   《饮酒歌》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                         </span>歌剧《茶花女》选段</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                演唱：谢琳<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>张向华</span></p>
